  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Breakfast</strong> is buffet style and served from 7.30- 9.30am. Expect a good selection of things like fresh fruit, pastries, cereals, bread, cheese, cold cuts, teas and coffees. There's also some hot options like eggs and bacon. </p>
<p>Guests choosing half board dine at the restaurant between 7 - 9pm. The menu changes daily and you'll have a choice of three courses plus a salad buffet.</p>
<p><strong>Panoramic Restaurant </strong>serves traditional Sicilian cuisine as well as international dishes with a different menu option each day with a salad and vegetable buffet. Guest staying on a bed and breakfast board basis can also dine here and choose from the a la carte menu. Open 7 - 9pm. </p>
<p><strong>American Bar </strong>with its large terrace, is the ideal place for an aperitivo or cocktail. </p>
<p><strong>Snack Bar </strong>serving light lunch and snacks. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
