  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pools &amp; Beaches</strong></span></p>
<p>Outdoor salt water swimming pool, Open 9am - 6pm. Pool towels can be hired for approx. €3 per towel. </p>
<p>There's direct access to the sea from the hotel - a ladder attached to the volcanic rocks, gives access straight into the deep water. If you'd prefer, the fine sandy beach of Gardini Naxos is only about 15 minutes' walk from the hotel. Some parts of the beach are public, but other parts have private beach clubs which are payable locally. </p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Laundry service (payable locally)</li>
<li>Free private parking </li>
<li>Free WiFi in the common areas</li>
</ul>
<p>A local bus service to and from <a data-udi="umb://document/919b72992bd64fd4a35a60df994feff6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/919b72992bd64fd4a35a60df994feff6}" title="Taormina Area">Taormina</a> runs from the roundabout near to the hotel. Please note that this service only runs during the day. </p>]]></facilityDescription>
